ll obligations. In today&#39;s world of uncertain financial situation 3-Business has become a real opportunity for investors, partners and entrepreneurs to earn money. Our company provides such conditions by its responsibility and consistency. We invite you to get acquainted with them.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Sincerely yours,<br />\r\n3-Business company team.</p>', '2015-02-07 02:24:37', '2015-11-19 02:24:37'),
(28, 'BTC Plaza - 80 Days Online', 'btc-plaza-80-days-online', 1, '<p>Hi Everyone,<br />\r\nI am Ruben Leblanc and the Chief Executive of BTC Plaza. I would like to sum up our few months of work.<br />\r\nWe are online 80 days young and still only just starting to get going.... BTC Plaza is now the No.1 investment product in many people&#39;s portfolio and it seems there is no stopping the juggernaut from racing to greater heights.<br />\r\nTraffic is up, we should break through into the top 100,000 sites in the world this week with Alexa.<br />\r\nMembership is up, with at least 60 people joining every day.<br />\r\nInvestments are up, with $5000 of dollars in every day and most importantly, payments are UP, with over $24,640.61 of withdrawals already.<br />\r\nBTC Plaza - Your Successful Manager! BTC Plaza is based in United Kingdom wit h the registration number: 09247709. It is a company that brings together people who are related to finance for several years. BTC Plaza has been established to manage the funds of the company&#39;s clients. In other words, we apply our specialists&#39; asset management skills in serving the needs of our customers worldwide. We provide full range of investment management solutions for both amateur and senior investors.<br />\r\nNow we are available on<br />\r\nFacebook - https://www.facebook.com/BTCPLAZADirectLimited,<br />\r\nTwitter - https://twitter.com/btc_plaza<br />\r\nVkontakte - http://vk.com/id293685307.<br />\r\nWe are pleased to announce that we have a live chat that serves customers 24 hours&nbsp;a day, 7 days a week.<br />\r\nWe have telephone support in English by calling +44 203 6958890.<br />\r\nYou can keep track of our news and observe the changes.<br />\r\nIf you have any questions don&#39;t hesitate to contact our Support Center. We are a team of professionals with many years of experience that we gained at universities around the world. Now we enter the Internet in order to enable people around the world possibility to make money without the necessary risks and wasting time. Our company is open to all ideas and suggestions about us. We are waiting for any comments posted by you.&nbsp;<br />\r\nIn conclusion I can say that everything is moving in the right direction.<br />\r\nOur security systems work impeccably. We invite new investors to familiarize themselves with our offer. Those who have already registered in our program, we invite to start investing. In March you can enjoy the news - we go out of our new advertising campaign.<br />\r\nThanks to your funds, you can make your life becomes easier, and you will become wealthier. All in a simple and clear steps. Try!<br />\r\nIf you want to keep up, stay up to our news.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Best Regards,<br />\r\nRuben Lablanc<br />\r\nhttps://btcplaza.biz<br />\r\nBTC Plaza - Your Successful Manager!</p>', '2015-03-02 01:24:33', '2015-11-19 01:35:45'),
(29, 'How to understand the cash flow of 120 Profit Ltd!', 'how-to-understand-the-cash-flow-of-120-profit-ltd', 1, '<p>Dear Investors,</p>\r\n\r\n<p>120 Profit Ltd has developped rapidly during the past month.Now we are one of most search site in allhyipmonitors.com and allmonitors.net.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Fast develpopment give us more capital power also co-exist the risk. To control capital flowing is the sucess key of a company. Now the risk management system of 120 Profit Ltd has been set up, and is real time displaying in the home page for our investors.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Here we would like to explain how to understand our system:<br />\r\nTotal Deposit: The total deposit from our investors<br />\r\nTotal Paid: The total withdraw of system<br />\r\nTotal Captial: Basically it means cash reserve of our system. Total capial = Total deposit + Forex trading profit - Total withdraw.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In addition you can see the real time last 5 deposit, 5 withdrawal, top 5 investors at the bottom of our home page.<br />\r\n120 Profit is bulit in a transparent and win-win mode.Thanks again for our investor! If you have any doubt, do not hesitate to connect.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Sincerely,<br />\r\n120 Profit Team<br />\r\nwww.120profit.com</p>', '2015-03-09 01:33:20', '2015-11-19 01:33:20'),
