(40, '3 Effective Ways to find the right HYIP Program', '3-effective-ways-to-find-the-right-hyip-program', 2, '<p>Investing online could mean both things &ndash; either you could make profits when you invest smartly, or you could lose all if you overlook all the steps explained in this article.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Are you serious about investing online? If yes, we suggest you perform a thorough research and learn which HYIP are genuine and stay away from &ldquo;scam artists&rdquo;.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Here are few tips to help you find the right HYIP program:</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step #1 Do your homework</strong> &ndash; If you&rsquo;re serious about making profits through online investment, find a reliable HYIP program. Visit HYIP monitor sites such as <a href="http://sharehyip.com">ShareHYIP.com</a> where you&rsquo;ll find the list of all popular HYIP sites. You can get in-depth information about each, compare one against the other, and participate in those HYIP programs that suit your individual investment goals.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step #2 Check the status (payout report) of each program</strong> &ndash; Next, consider finding out whether the HYIP program is making payments or has stopped paying recently. For this, visit HYIP monitor sites and HYIP forums to check the status/payout reports of each program.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In addition, make sure to notice number of days the site ran (lower the number, higher the profits).</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step #3 Sign up to create HYIP account</strong> &ndash; Once you&rsquo;ve found the &ldquo;right&rdquo; HYIP program, sign up to create an account. Make sure to use a different (new) email, username, and password while creating an account on HYIP site. This will ensure your personal accounts won&rsquo;t be hacked by a sneaky admin.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Some words of warning:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Online investment is a risky business. Make sure the money you might lose after investing won&rsquo;t affect you overall.</li>\r\n	<li>Start small and increase the investing bigger as you become an experienced investor. For example, if you choose to invest on a HYIP that offers at least 1%-2% daily, invest only $200-$300, nothing more than that. Not only you&rsquo;ll prevent yourself being &ldquo;scammed&rdquo; (if the program turns out to be a fraud), but you&rsquo;ll also likely recuperate your losses without going bankrupt.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Effective HYIP Investing Tips for Beginners</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Investing in recently added HYIP program may help you earn more earnings. So make sure you look at the &ldquo;latest added HYIP program&rdquo; section on all HYIP monitoring sites to find latest paying HYIP.</li>\r\n	<li>Next, make a goal to earn back your initial investment. This will make you worry less about losing your money in case the HYIP admin closes down their business.</li>\r\n	<li>To avoid investing in non-paying (scam) HYIP program, visit all popular HYIP monitoring sites. These HYIP monitors usually maintain a list of genuine and high paying HYIP program. Read their reviews of each program, talk to the members there in order to get unbiased information.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Visit our <a href="http://sharehyip.com/blog">blog</a> section to read more helpful (free) tips on online investment at <a href="http://sharehyip.com">ShareHYIP.com</a>.</p>', '2014-01-23 00:16:00', '2015-01-23 00:16:00'),
(41, 'HYIP Investment Tips for Beginners', 'hyip-investment-tips-for-beginners', 2, '<p>Investing on online HYIP program will make you wealth, but if you&rsquo;re NOT careful you can lose badly, especially when you&rsquo;re a newbie.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Before you even think about getting serious about investing online, make sure to research properly to find the best HYIP program so that you actually make huge ROI.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><em><strong>Here are few HYIP investment tips for beginners:</strong></em></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Research to find the best HYIP program &ndash; Before investing online, do your research to know which HYIP program are high paying and which are simply &ldquo;<del>SCAMS</del>,&rdquo; just waiting to take all of your hard-earned money.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>It&rsquo;s also important to understand the difference between poorly performing HYIPs and the scammers. Although poorly performing HYIPs may NOT make you more profits, but scam programs will surely cost all your hard-earned money, time, and energy. You need to stay away from them. Period!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Next, know when a good paying HYIP is about to crash down, too.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>By performing a thorough research, you will be aware of the market, learn to identify the right HYIP program to invest, and know when and how to invest.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>For this, make a habit of visiting HYIP Monitor , once or twice a week.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Here, you can learn about the most popular HYIP programs in the market, check their performance during the past few years, and check their investment status, among other things.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;Learn about the current trends &ndash; Investment trends could be good as well as bad. While good trends will help you earn profits, bad trends will only cost you money.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Here&rsquo;s how to identify a good trend that will actually make you money:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1. A good trend is obvious and doesn&rsquo;t last too long. A seemingly good HYIP program that keeps on rising on the charts is a &ldquo;stale green light&rdquo; for you &ndash; it will likely crash down as soon as it starts the downward path.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>2. On the other hand, a bad trend that suddenly spikes up in the income chart is just a hoax that cunning investors would like you to believe and invest in.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>3. There are different kinds of people. Some are superstitious and they use it to determine what to do in certain situations, which usually work for them. Although it&rsquo;s difficult to accurately predict the future of stocks depending upon luck and superstition, but often times it works for a lot of people.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>4. Do not pay attention to the graphs you see on the investment charts. Instead pay attention to what&rsquo;s going on around you. You&rsquo;ll likely notice latest trends floating around that could be worthy of a long term investment. By paying attention to what people are saying, wearing, and doing, you will be in a better position to predict how a particular stock will do.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><em>Take Calculated Risks &ndash; HYIPs can make you money only if you&rsquo;re willing to invest in it.</em></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>According to a study, the most profitable programs are usually the most risky. This doesn&rsquo;t mean we do NOT want you to invest in other safer HYIP programs, though. In fact, a wide range of investment portfolio will make your more experienced and an all-round investor who can make wise decisions on almost all types of investing scenario.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>But if you&rsquo;re unwilling to take a risk, maybe you should look other safer ways to make money, not HYIP investment program.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>CONCLUSION</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Remember that HYIP investing could be upsetting, but that is just its nature. The more risky the program, the better you&rsquo;ll do. The best way to earn more profits through HYIPs is to actually visit&nbsp;<a href="http://sharehyip.com/">HYIP Monitor.</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href="http://sharehyip.com/">HYIP Monitor</a>&nbsp;contains helpful guide, reviews, and customer ratings that will make the process of identifying the right HYIP program easy and fast for you.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Are you ready to make your first HYIP investment?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Visit <a href="http://sharehyip.com/">ShareHYIP.com</a>&nbsp;for the best guide.</p>', '2014-01-31 03:21:00', '2014-01-31 03:21:00'),
(42, 'How to Choose a Right HYIP Program that Will Make You Money', 'how-to-choose-a-right-hyip-program-that-will-make-you-money', 2, '<p>It is true that investing through HYIP site/program will help you make money online. But it is also true that the internet is crammed with many fraudulent HYIP investment sites, and hence, choosing a reliable and legitimate HYIP site could be difficult.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Here are few helpful tips to help you avoid the scammers and find the right HYIP program that will build you wealth:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Check the graphics.</strong>&nbsp;Check the graphic design on the HYIP site. If the HYIP site contains primitive designs &mdash; simplified fonts and outdated effects and styles &mdash; the site was probably designed with a short term view.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>On the other hand, online investment sites that uses fresh design elements &ndash; banners, logo, website design &ndash; indicates that they&rsquo;re active and spend significant amount of their profits on marketing and advertisement efforts, another reason why you need to invest with them.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>The Legend.</strong>&nbsp;The legend of the project will tell you where and how these HYIP site make their payments to their members. Do they generate income through investment in stocks, jewelry, gold, Forex market, medicines? Or do they generate income through a single source, like only from stock market?</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Similarly, the income has to be clear and declared by an existing investor. Vague income description is an indication of serious problems.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Income Charged.</strong>&nbsp;Exchange works only during weekdays. Some investors have been complaining HYIP programs charging them during even during the holidays and on weekends. Stay away from them.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Daily profits.&nbsp;</strong>Do their members/investors get paid daily? If they do, are they able to withdraw their earnings, anytime?</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Withdrawing profits daily means reduced risks for investors. If HYIP site owners refuse to display their earning, let&rsquo;s say, for more than a month, that&rsquo;s a red flag you need to be wary of.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Ease of communication.</strong>&nbsp;A legitimate and paying HYIP site has contact numbers, email address, valid office address, and sometimes even have a 24/hr customer support system (online chat) displayed prominently on their site.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>An anonymous contact form, on the other hand, is a serious problem. Contact the owners before investing.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Mandatory documents.</strong>&nbsp;Do these sites include proper legal, registration, and licensing documents on their site? Their willingness to do their business legally makes them more genuine and favorable over those who remain &ldquo;shady&rdquo; in the activities.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Maximum profit percentage.</strong>&nbsp;What&rsquo;s their maximum profit percentage? Do you know their profits type &ndash; fixed or floating?</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>If the HYIP site boasts of more than 2% profits share to its members, be cautious investing there. No matter how successful the company may be, why would anyone pay such a large amount of profits to their investors?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>If they proposed profit type is floating, it may indicate they&rsquo;re genuine company to invest in. Sometimes, there could be days when the profit percentage could be constant, however, for longer period of time (150+ trading days); the profits made during good times could compensate all the low profits made during bad days.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>News Updates and Online Support.</strong>&nbsp;A legitimate HYIP site always updates their site with fresh news and notifications, on a weekly basis. They&rsquo;re also available for a quick support, whether via an email or an online support.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Do you need help choosing the right HYIP program to invest?&nbsp;<a href="http://sharehyip.com/contact">Contact us</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href="http://sharehyip.com/blog">Click here</a>&nbsp;to visit our site to read more helpful tips and strategies on HYIP programs.</p>', '2014-02-11 13:09:23', '2014-02-11 13:09:23'),
(43, 'Investing on HYIP Site? Consider these 7 things before Investing', 'investing-on-hyip-site-consider-these-7-things-before-investing', 2, '<p>Are you trying to invest in HYIP site? Here are 7 time-tested and proven rules (strategies) you need to consider before you make an investment decision and stay away from &ldquo;scam artists.&rdquo;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>What is HYIPs? HYIP, or High Yield Investment Program, is one of the investment vehicles where investors make money by investing in high yield and high risk market.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In HYIP programs, investors from around the world collaborate and invest money and share profits later. Most established HYIP sites pay their investors on a daily, weekly, and sometimes, even on monthly basis, online.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>But making money through HYIP program isn&rsquo;t an easy walk in the park, though.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>While most first-time investors either lack proper investment funding, others simply do NOT have right tools and proper knowledge to make it big in this type of investment market. In addition, there are &ldquo;scammers&rdquo; who are only interested to after people&rsquo;s hard-earn money.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Consider these 7 things to ensure you&rsquo;ll make better decisions and find the right program that fits your needs.</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li><strong>Online Support</strong>\r\n\r\n	<p>Once you&rsquo;re on a HYIP site, check to see if they have an established customer support service for investors. A well-established and serious HYIP site will have contact numbers, online ticket system, quick contact options &mdash; e-mail, contact forms, online chat, etc &mdash; prominently displayed on their site.</p>\r\n\r\n	<p>Other HYIP sites will also likely have their representatives from around the world.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Online security</strong>\r\n	<p>A genuine HYIP site puts importance to online security. They often have a well-established system to protect against DDOS attacks. Others use SSL certificate to offer a secure place for online transactions. For example, paying HYIP sites have a secure page(s) (with a &ldquo;padlock sign&rdquo; at the taskbar) that are secure to conduct online payments.</p>\r\n\r\n	<p>Also check if the site is verified with the Merchant. A trust score over 50+ is a good indication of a reliable program.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Copyright Info</strong>\r\n	<p>Next, check to see if the HYIP site is copyrighted. Do they have a link to a copyright page visible on every web page on their site? If not, you must be cautious.</p>\r\n\r\n	<p>Other thing to consider is the copyright info. Does the year exceed the current year. For example, do you see &ldquo;<strong>Copyright @ 2010-2015</strong>?&rdquo;</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Web Copy Errors</strong>\r\n	<p>You found a HYIP site on Google. You read through their description and it compelled you to click through the search result. Now, you&rsquo;re reading the home page content to know more about &ldquo;who they are&rdquo; and &ldquo;what they offer.&rdquo; Suddenly, you spot a spelling error, &ldquo;Invseetment&rdquo; on the headline. Would not you be cautious spending your hard-earned money here?</p>\r\n\r\n	<p>There are plenty of junk sites that have poorly written copy &mdash; with disorganized content that only seems to confuse the readers. If this is the case, look somewhere else.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Weekly News Updates</strong>\r\n	<p>An active HYIP site always has interesting things to share with their investors/members. An outdated and scam site, on the other hand, doesn&rsquo;t have anything new to say because&nbsp;<em>do NOT</em>&nbsp;like to stay active.</p>\r\n\r\n	<p>Read the website&rsquo;s &ldquo;news&rdquo; section to ensure they&rsquo;re publishing fresh news and updates to their members, every month, if not every week.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Social Network</strong>\r\n	<p>Do you know why some HYIP site do&nbsp;<em>NOT</em>&nbsp;care to open a FREE account on most popular social media sites like Facebook and Twitter? Because they aren&rsquo;t for a long haul and they do<em>&nbsp;NOT</em>&nbsp;want to get exposed.</p>\r\n\r\n	<p>On the other hand, a legitimate paying HYIP sites do have accounts on Facebook, Twitter, LinkedIn, Google+, and they do have an admin to manage their accounts, too.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Monthly Newsletters</strong>\r\n	<p>A HYIP site that sends monthly newsletters to their members is a good indication for you. They always like to keep their investors/ members with up-to-date market news, trends, and best tips and strategies to help their members make even better investment decisions.</p>\r\n\r\n	<p>Other HYIP sites also take time to send newsletters on important holidays and festivals, like New Year and Christmas, just to keep building a lasting relationship with their members.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p>Although there are plenty of things you need to consider before investing in HYIP program, these 7 tips will help you identify a genuine HYIP program/site that will make you wealth.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Do you need help finding the right HYIP program to invest?&nbsp;<a href="http://sharehyip.com/contact">Contact us</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href="http://sharehyip.com/blog">Click here</a>&nbsp;to visit our site to read more helpful tips and strategies on HYIP programs.</p>', '2014-02-19 06:13:00', '2014-02-19 06:13:00'),
(44, 'Top 3 HYIP Investment Tips', 'top-3-hyip-investment-tips', 2, '<p>Do you want to learn more about HYIP Investment before making your first investment move? If you&rsquo;re considering online investment, there are 3 top things you need to be aware of so that you avoid all the pitfall of the HYIP industry and focus your energy on things that will help you get high ROI.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>What is HYIP, anyway</em>?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>HYIP is short term for &ldquo;High Yield Investment Program.&rdquo; Many investors today participate on HYIP programs because it yields them higher interest than any other normal saving accounts.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Most investment gurus believe that HYIP can be a lucrative income generating venture, but investing in the &lsquo;<del>wrong</del>&rsquo; HYIP program (programs that seem too good to be true) could lead to financial disaster. As with all types of investment, these top 3 investment strategies will try to reject any hypes and &lsquo;fake&rsquo; HYIP programs that take away people&rsquo;s hard-earned money.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Once you go through each step, you&rsquo;ll end up with a genuine &lsquo;paying&rsquo; HYIP program that will make you money.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Top 3 HYIP Investment tips that will save you money:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Analyze the Market Condition.</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Before you even think investing in online investment programs such as HYIP, first consider the &lsquo;market performance&rsquo; in terms of ROI and interest. For example, try to examine the average return on investment in both high-end investment program and lowest-end investment program.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Once you know the estimate average return percentage of the HYIP market, compare it against the average ROI percentage of your potential HYIP program. If the RETURNS lie significantly outside of the expected market returns, consider it a &lsquo;red&rsquo; flag and move on.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Find another HYIP investment program that offers more valid returns. For more information, visit sites like&nbsp;<a href="http://sharehyip.com/">ShareHYIP.com</a>&nbsp;to find genuine &lsquo;paying&rsquo; HYIP programs.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Thoroughly Research.</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Next thing you must do to avoid investing in &lsquo;<del>wrong</del>&rsquo; HYIP program is to find the ones that are genuine. For this, do a thorough research about the HYIP program listed on&nbsp;<a href="http://sharehyip.com/">HYIP monitor site</a>&nbsp;to learn their company&rsquo;s profile, their past performance, and any other credentials that convinced you to join and invest.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>If you do NOT see any references of past projects, or you do not see them listed on HYIP monitoring sites, that&rsquo;s an indication of a fraudulent investment program.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>If the only way to contact the owners is through e-mail and Internet and there isn&rsquo;t a clear way to contact the support to get your questions answered, we recommend that you walk away and look for other program.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Start with small investment.</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>The final tip in HYIP investment program is to start small and be careful while investing. Until you have learned all the basics of online investment and learned major the pitfalls that most beginners make, do not be tempted to invest BIG no matter how great the end results seem to you.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Instead, invest small amount and wait till the next 1-3 months to monitor the performance of your investment. Only when you see steady ROI, then only you should consider investing bigger. Just like any other investment industry, the amount of make you a savvy investor.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>For more free HYIP investment tips, read our&nbsp;<a href="http://sharehyip.com/blog">blog</a>.</p>', '2014-02-25 03:27:12', '2014-02-25 03:27:12');
